  <!--Riot Gear here temporarily while testing decals-->
  <ThingDef ParentName="ArmorHelmetMakeableBase">
    <defName>EOTF_RiotCarapaceHelmet</defName>
    <label>Riot Helmet</label>
    <description>A leather made clone of the carapace helmet. Reinforced with a few steel plates it provides a decent level of protection. Most of the time though it is found in the hands of law enforcement, who often point toards the start on the forehead and use it as a means of extracting graft from the locals. Just to think that the wear only a few years ago was failing his high school exams because they didn't believe that those skills would be practical. Look at them now, the government gave them a gun and carte blanche on whatever they do!</description>
    <recipeMaker>
      <researchPrerequisite>EOTF_RiotArmor</researchPrerequisite>
      <unfinishedThingDef>UnfinishedTechArmor</unfinishedThingDef>
      <skillRequirements>
        <Crafting>7</Crafting>
